## 13. Open Items / Future Considerations

- **Team sharing** — the Quarter Map PDF and posture statement should eventually be shareable with team members as a one-page quarterly brief. Not in scope for this build.
- **Quarter-over-quarter comparison** — future consideration: show how this quarter's selections compare to last quarter's to surface the evolution of focus over time.
- **Sprint Planning seed** — the locked 3P selections must be available as seed data in Sprint Planning so capability areas pre-populate as initiative containers. This handoff should be confirmed as part of the Sprint Planning build.
- **Observational readback — deferred** — the real-time observational layer during selection is not feasible without live GPT calls and is parked. If introduced in a future phase, it belongs only in the completion synthesis, not during active selection.